snippet.title: Dead Pets Unleashed - Official Gameplay Trailer | The MIX Showcase October 2023
snippet.description:
Check out gameplay from various mini-games you'll discover in Dead Pets Unleashed, a narrative game coming to PC, Nintendo Switch, Xbox, and PlayStation 5. A demo is available now on PC and Xbox. 

Struggling punk rock band, Dead Pets, is looking for their big break. Play rhythm games at band practice, work a diner shift, converse with characters, and manage Gordy’s life in this feminist, slice-of-life, management-lite, and minigame-heavy story game.
